            "title": "A股半日跌轉升  近高位收市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股跌轉升，滬股半日高位收市，兩市成交9762.87億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指收升8點或0.21%，報3883點，為半日高位，今早開報3870，跌5點或0.13%，早段見3856點，跌19點或0.49%，為上午低位，隨即向上轉升，以半日高位收市，半日成交3920.23億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報12967點，升92點或0.72%，今早開報12869，跌6點或0.05%，早段見12834，跌41點或0.32%，即節節向上，臨近收市見12982，升107點或0.83%，半日成交5842.64億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日升10點或0.23%，報4525點 ; 創業板指數升21點或0.71%，報3052點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15463999-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%87-%e8%bf%91%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82",
